title: Cyber Cafe
alt: Since we haven't really settled on a name for those online hangout/work spaces that try to recreate the experience of cafes, and I love confusion, I'm going to start calling them 'cyber cafes' or 'internet cafes.'
transcript:
Which word in the name "cyber cafe" sounds more dated?2015 - Cyber
2016 - Cyber
2017 - Cyber
2018 - Cyber
2019 - Cyber
2020 - Cafe
